After the positive vibes that greeted his debut single, ‘My Head,’ in 2021, John Lucky Oghenevwerhe aka Loverboy has released another hit single, ‘Igbese.’ Currently enjoying rave reviews across the country and beyond, ‘Igbese,’ is the latest offering from Loverboy after his emergence on TikTok.   2baba, Rema, Cavemen, set to thrill fans on Afrikashrine TV     Why I returned to school, by Zaaki Azzay     Kizz Daniel secures double deal   Since the release of his current project, the Delta-born singer has been headlining major shows and concerts across Lagos, one of which is the recently organised Beat FM NYSC Concert. Loverboy performed excellently to the admiration of music lovers with his current single, Igbese, leaving the fans further impressed. Recently, during a live radio interview, the soft-spoken musician revealed among other things that he looks forward to rewarding his fans with electrifying collabos with some of the industry’s front-liners doing well within and outside the continent.